rs":["\\CT[1]女子喘息的说着，脸上都是红晕... ..."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]那丰满的胸部，粉嫩的乳头让人无法移开眼睛。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",1,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]官二代：这是什么回事？这就女人好不要脸...但是我的肉棒好硬。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",3,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]铁匠：我从来没看到过如此漂亮的胸部，快让俺摸摸！！！"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",3,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]乞丐：比那醉仙楼的头牌的奶子都淫荡！！！"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",1,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]官二代：说的你看过似得。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]顿时众人呵呵呵大笑，双眼却死死的盯着\\n[1]那丰满的胸部。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]众人你看我，我看你，都不敢做第一人，生怕这女子大叫，引来了衙役。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]但是被一群人看的感觉，让\\n[1]有些尴尬，害羞，想跑，那些灼热的眼光想要把她吃干抹净一般。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]但是看着众人痴迷的样子，\\n[1]心里勇气一丝丝小骄傲，甚至在看到有人的鸡儿勃起，她害羞的想跑。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]但是身体不受自己控制，\\n[1]又羞涩又气，那些雄性的气息围绕着她，她温热的蜜穴都开始流出汁水。"]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,"47-KZLUXB2",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]\\n[1]：（好羞耻，自己居然湿了。）"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]甜蜜又芳香的汁水在衣服内，顺着大腿缓缓流下，羞耻的\\n[1]闭上了双眼。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]\\n[1]：（都怪我不够强，被人弄成这样，若有哪天，我足够强大，定要一雪前耻。）"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,"、"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]\\n[1]：（一定要杀了他... ...）"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]虽然这样说，即便道心如何强硬，这样长时间的羞耻举动，让\\n[1]的道心都忍不住动摇。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]远处黑暗中的身影笑嘻嘻的看着，摸着下巴，对着众人使用了仙法。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]秦正经：初次就到这里，玩坏了就没有意思了。"]},{"code":221,"indent":0,"parameters":[]},{"code":235,"indent":0,"parameters":[1]},{"code":122,"indent":0,"parameters":[4,4,1,0,2]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,1,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\n[1]只感觉睡了一觉，迷迷糊糊的睁开双眼，已经是白天。"]},{"code":121,"indent":0,"parameters":[18,18,1]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[53]},{"code":121,"indent":0,"parameters":[652,652,1]},{"code":122,"indent":0,"parameters":[703,703,0,0,1]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[9]},{"code":121,"indent":0,"parameters":[325,325,1]},{"code":201,"indent":0,"parameters":[0,93,5,4,2,0]},{"code":211,"indent":0,"parameters":[1]},{"code":223,"indent":0,"parameters":[[0,0,0,0],60,false]},{"code":222,"indent":0,"parameters":[]},{"code":0,"indent":0,"parameters":[]}],"moveFrequency":3,"moveRoute":{"list":[{"code":0,"parameters":[]}],"repeat":true,"skippable":false,"wait":false},"moveSpeed":3,"moveType":0,"priorityType":0,"stepAnime":false,